post_text: Conscious Discipline® has transformed the way we provide educational excellence. This framework for social emotional learning has scientific brain research proving that students must feel safe and loved before they can access their brilliance. We encourage parents to follow this page￼ to learn skills to help you support your child at home. #LESDConciousDiscipline
shared_text:
Conscious Discipline®
April 6 at 6:30 AM ·

In place of our "Conscious Commitment" this week, we are starting a "Brain Smart Start Series." Each day will feature a Master or Certified Instructor guiding you through the four activities (unite, disengage stress, connect and commit) to help you start your day the Brain Smart way!

Today, Dr. Becky Bailey is kicking off our series by sharing the background behind Brain Smart Starts. Join us tomorrow, and the rest of this week at 8:30 AM Central for a new Brain Smart Start you can do from the comfort of your own home! #iHeartCD #brainsmartstart
